Yes, the default config does have that (safe) behaviour. It&#x27;s rather easy to change, by replacing the vcl_recv function in the config. Something like:<p><pre><code>  sub vcl_recv {
    if (req.http.cookie ~ &quot;wordpress_logged_in_|comment_author_|wp-postpass_&quot;) {
      return (pass);
    }
    return (lookup);
  }</code></pre>
